连连炫 Project

为纪念炫大佬23岁生日，特制此游戏。
版权问题，图片和音乐资源未放在本repo。

操作说明：
鼠标左键 - 选择方块
鼠标右键 - 取消选择
M键 - 播放/停止背景音乐
R键 - 打乱所有方块
T键 - 显示提示
Q键 - 返回主菜单
Y键 - 游戏结束时再开一局


LianLianXuan Project

To memorize 23rd birthday of Boss Xuan, we developed this game.
Due to the copyright issue, all images, sound and music are NOT included in this repo.

Operations:
Left Click  - Select a block
Right Click - Cancel selection
M           - Play / Stop background music
R           - Randomize all existed blocks
T           - Give a tip
Q           - Return to main menu
Y           - Start a new game when game is ended